Package: eloquence
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, qemu-user-binfmt
Recommends: speech-dispatcher, curl, unzip, python3,
 gcc-arm-linux-gnueabihf, kmod
Description: Eloquence V6.1 text-to-speech engine
 Runs the ETI Eloquence V6.1 ARM TTS libraries under QEMU user-mode
 emulation. Includes a command-line tool, a drop-in libeci.so shim
 library, and a speech-dispatcher output module.
 .
 After installation, run 'sudo eloquence-setup' to download and
 configure the Eloquence voice data.
